annotation.text: Waits on a message from the RPA subprocess in Create Update Address. This is necessary to chain through the Address task and Task Completion nodes.

If the related record is closed, we don't create an error task because we don't want to reopen it, and instead rely solely on the customer alert to let the users know that this external address update failed.
